Effects of Credit Access - Credit Score Cutoffs (600 - 2018:2019)

08/08/2022

loans <- read_fst(path="/home/dimuthu/SSRN Oct 2021/Predictability/loans.fst",as.data.table = T)
loans[,application_month:=as.Date(paste0(year(application_date),"-",month(application_date),"-01"))]

1 Credit score cutoffs overtime

We use the 600 cutoff. Similar results using 620 cutoff, but not as robust. Sample size is too small to use 640 cutoff. Sample: 580 to 620 with subsequent credit reports around the 12 month mark.

minimum_fico <- loans[,
                      .(fico_1pct=quantile(fico_score,0.01,na.rm=T),
                        fico_half_pct=quantile(fico_score,0.005,na.rm=T)
                        ),
                      by=application_month]

minimum_fico[,fico_cutoff:=floor(fico_half_pct/5)*5]
minimum_fico[,fico_cutoff:=ifelse(fico_cutoff<620,600,ifelse(fico_cutoff==625,620,fico_cutoff))]

minimum_fico <- minimum_fico[!is.na(application_month)]


g1 <- ggplot(data=melt(minimum_fico[!is.na(application_month) & application_month<"2020-01-01"],id="application_month"),
             aes(x=application_month,y=value,color=variable))+
  scale_color_manual(
  labels = c("Credit score 1st percentile", "Credit score 0.5th percentile","Credit score cutoff"),
  values = c("darkturquoise","dodgerblue2","dodgerblue4"))+
  geom_line()+
  theme_minimal()+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom",legend.title = element_blank())+
  labs(x="Month",y="Credit score")

minimum_fico <- minimum_fico[,c("application_month","fico_cutoff")]

                      po.annual_income,
                      po.general_dq_reasons,

                      crs.fico_score,
                      crs.vantage_score,
                      crs.cleansed_vantage_score,
                      cr.individual_credit_history_days as credit_history,
                      cr.s0y2_birthdate_ccyymm as birthyear,
                      cr.at01_number_of_trades as number_of_accounts,
                      cr.num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months,
                      cr.num_accounts_opened_in_past_24_months,
                      cr.num_trade_accounts,
                      cr.num_trade_accounts_currently_delinquent,
                      cr.total_num_open_accounts,
                      cr.s207a_months_since_most_recent_tradeline_bankruptcy as bankruptcymonths1,
                      cr.s207s_months_since_most_recent_public_record_bankruptcy as bankruptcymonths2,
                      cr.at33a_total_balance_of_open_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as total_balance,
                      cr.num_inquiries_past_6_months as inquiries,
                      cr.bc101s_total_balance_of_all_credit_card_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as credit_card_balance,
                      cr.bc107s_number_of_30_and_60_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as cc_del_3060,
                      cr.bc108s_number_of_90_or_more_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as cc_del90,
                      cr.g007_number_of_30_day_or_worse_ratings_in_payment_pattern as pastdue30,
                      cr.g008_number_of_60_day_or_worse_ratings_in_payment_pattern as pastdue60,
                      cr.g043_number_of_trades_ever_90_or_more_days_past_due as any_del_12_months,
                      cr.mortgage_balance,
                      cr.revolving_balance,
                      cr.installment_balance,
                      cr.num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months,
                      cr.percent_of_revolving_credit_utilized,
                      cr.at21_months_since_most_recent_trade_opened,
                      cr.g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent,
                      cr.g301s_worst_rating_on_credit_card_trades,
                      cr.bc34s_utilization_for_open_credit_card_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as creditcard_utilization
    FROM monolith.upstart_applications as ua
    LEFT JOIN monolith.user_applications as usera
    on usera.upstart_application_id = ua.id
    LEFT JOIN monolith.pricings as pr
    on usera.upstart_id = pr.upstart_id
    LEFT JOIN monolith.pricing_outputs as po
    on po.pricing_id = pr.id
    LEFT JOIN monolith.credit_report_summaries as crs
    on crs.user_account_id = usera.user_account_id
    LEFT JOIN transunion.credit_reports as cr
    on crs.credit_report_id = cr.id
    where 
    pr.pricing_reason='initial' and
    pr.applied_at::date=ua.created_at::date and
    crs.reason = 'initial' and
    cr.fico_score>=550 and 
    cr.fico_score<=680 and
    crs.pull_date >='2016-06-01'
"
)


apps <- apps[abs(as.numeric(created_at-pull_date))<30]
apps <- apps[!duplicated(apps$upstart_id)]
apps[,funded:=ifelse(decision_status=="funded",1,0)]
apps[,mortgage_pct:=mortgage_balance/(total_balance+1)]
apps[,revolving_pct:=revolving_balance/(total_balance+1)]
apps[,appyear:=year(created_at)]
apps[,birthyear:=as.numeric(substr(birthyear,5,8))]
apps[,borrower_age:=appyear-birthyear]
apps[,credit_history:=floor(credit_history/365)]
apps[,application_month:=as.Date(paste0(year(applied_at),"-",month(applied_at),"-01"))]

apps <- merge(apps,minimum_fico,by="application_month")
apps[,distance_cutoff:=fico_score-fico_cutoff]
apps <- apps[fico_cutoff<640]

years <- 2018:2019

2 Kink in approval rate around 600 credit score cutoff

funded_mean <- apps[fico_cutoff==cutoff  & fico_score %in% (cutoff-20):(cutoff+20) & appyear %in% years & dti<50 & inquiries<2& ! bankruptcymonths2 %in% 0:36 & num_trade_accounts_currently_delinquent==0 & num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months<=2,.(funded=mean(funded,na.rm=T)),by=fico_score]
funded_mean[,D:=ifelse(fico_score>=cutoff,1,0)]

regs <- list()
regs[[1]] <- lm(funded~D*fico_score,data=funded_mean[!fico_score %in% 595:602])
funded_mean[,predfunded:=predict(regs[[1]],funded_mean)]

ggplot()+
  geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==0],aes(x=fico_score,y=predfunded),color="dodgerblue4")+
  geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==1],aes(x=fico_score,y=predfunded),color="dodgerblue4")+
  geom_point(data=funded_mean,aes(x=fico_score,y=funded),color="dodgerblue2")+
  theme_minimal()+
  labs(x="Credit score",y="Fraction of loans funded")

3 No discontinuity or kink in other variables

control_vars <- c("dti","annual_income","borrower_age","credit_history","total_balance","number_of_accounts","inquiries")
control_var_labs <- c("Debt-to-income","Income","Age","Credit history","Total balance","No accounts","No inquiries")

g <- list()
for(i in 1:length(control_vars)) {
  
  eval(parse(text=paste0("funded_mean <- apps[fico_cutoff==cutoff  & fico_score %in% (cutoff-20):(cutoff+20) & appyear %in% years & annual_income<200000 & dti<100,.(var=mean(",control_vars[i],",na.rm=T)),by=fico_score]")))
  funded_mean[,D:=ifelse(fico_score>=cutoff,1,0)]
  
  regs <- list()
  regs[[1]] <- lm(var~D+poly(fico_score,2),data=funded_mean)
  funded_mean[,predvar:=predict(regs[[1]],funded_mean)]
  
  g[[i]] <- ggplot()+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==0],aes(x=fico_score,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==1],aes(x=fico_score,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_point(data=funded_mean,aes(x=fico_score,y=var),color="dodgerblue2")+
            theme_minimal()+
            geom_vline(xintercept = cutoff,color="gray50")+
            theme(text = element_text(size=8))
  
  if(i>=6) {
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="Credit score",y=control_var_labs[i])
  } else{
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="",y=control_var_labs[i])
  }
  
}

grid.arrange(g[[1]],g[[2]],g[[3]],g[[4]],g[[5]],g[[6]],g[[7]],nrow=4)

4 Graphical evidence

control_vars <- c("cc_del","fico_change","new_mortgage")
control_var_labs <- c("Credit card delinq.","Credit score change","New mortgage")

g <- list()
for(i in 1:length(control_vars)) {
  
  eval(parse(text=paste0("funded_mean <- regsample[fico_score %in% (cutoff-20):(cutoff+20) ,.(var=mean(",control_vars[i],",na.rm=T)),by=fico_score]")))
  funded_mean[,D:=ifelse(fico_score>=cutoff,1,0)]
  
  regs <- list()
  regs[[1]] <- lm(var~D*poly(fico_score,1),data=funded_mean)
  funded_mean[,predvar:=predict(regs[[1]],funded_mean)]
  
  g[[i]] <- ggplot()+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==0],aes(x=fico_score,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==1],aes(x=fico_score,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_point(data=funded_mean,aes(x=fico_score,y=var),color="dodgerblue2")+
            theme_minimal()+
            geom_vline(xintercept = cutoff,color="gray50")+
            theme(text = element_text(size=8))
  
  if(i>=2) {
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="Months since bankruptcy",y=control_var_labs[i])
  } else{
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="",y=control_var_labs[i])
  }
  
}

grid.arrange(g[[1]],g[[2]],g[[3]],nrow=2)

5 RDD: Kernal-2nd degree, bankwidth-full sample

formula_rdd <- "D*distance_bin|monthssinceapp+application_month|0|application_month"
bandwidth = 20

r <- list()
r[[1]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("cc_del~",formula_rdd)),data=regsample[abs(distance_to_cutoff)<bandwidth ])
r[[2]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("fico_change~",formula_rdd)),data=regsample[abs(distance_to_cutoff)<bandwidth])
r[[3]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("new_mortgage~",formula_rdd)),data=regsample[abs(distance_to_cutoff)<bandwidth])

stargazer(r,no.space = T,align = T,omit.stat=c("ser","rsq"),style = "qje",omit.table.layout = "n", 
          dep.var.labels = rep(c("Credit card delinq","Credit score change","Mortgage"),2),
          add.lines=list(c("Month,Months since app","Y","Y","Y","Y")),
          type="text")#

6 RDD: Kernal-2nd degree, bankwidth - full sample

formula_rdd <- "D*distance_to_cutoff+log(1+annual_income)+dti+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries)+log(1+total_balance)+log(1+credit_history)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+log(1+creditcard_utilization*100)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|monthssinceapp+application_month|0|application_month"

formula_rdd2 <- "D*distance_to_cutoff+log(1+annual_income)+dti+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries)+log(1+total_balance)+log(1+credit_history)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+creditcard_utilization*100)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|monthssinceapp+application_month|0|application_month"

bandwidth = 20

r <- list()

r[[2]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("fico_change~",formula_rdd)),data=regsample[abs(distance_to_cutoff)<bandwidth])
